snippet.title: Raskulls Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Raskulls is an upcoming action platformer game for Xbox Live Arcade. With a massive single player Mega Quest adventure and four-player online and local multiplayer, Raskulls is set to join the heritage of the most popular XBLA games and charm the world with the hilarious cast of characters!
